---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | 5.Y"
  description="5.Y Privacy Policy - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data. GDPR and SOC 2 compliant."
  canonicalUrl="https://www.five-whys.com/privacy"
  activeNav=""
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="pt-16 px-8 pb-8 text-center bg-bg-secondary border-b border-border-theme">
      <h1 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-medium tracking-[-0.02em] mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg">How we collect, use, and protect your personal information.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-8 pt-12 pb-20">
      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-medium text-text-primary mt-10 mb-4">The Basics</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">At 5Y Holdings Pte. Ltd. (5.Y), we respect your privacy and are committed to safeguarding your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data in compliance with global privacy regulations, including GDPR and PDPA.</p>

      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-medium text-text-primary mt-10 mb-4">What We Collect</h2>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">We use cookies and similar tools to enhance your experience and analyze website traffic. Cookies are small text files stored on your device, allowing us to understand visitor behavior and improve our services.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Personal Data</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">If you contact us through forms, we may collect details like your name, email address, and message to respond to your inquiries.</p>

      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-medium text-text-primary mt-10 mb-4">How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-3">Your information is used solely for:</p>
      <ul class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6 pl-6 flex flex-col gap-2">
        <li>Enhancing website performance and improving user experience.</li>
        <li>Responding to inquiries or fulfilling requests submitted via the website.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties unless required by law.</p>

      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-medium text-text-primary mt-10 mb-4">Opt-Out of Tracking</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">You can manage cookies and other tracking methods via the cookie setting on your first visit to the website, or via your browser settings. To opt out of website analytics tracking, such as Google Analytics, you may use the Google Analytics Opt-Out browser add-on.</p>

      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-medium text-text-primary mt-10 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-3">As part of our commitment to privacy, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6 pl-6 flex flex-col gap-2">
        <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal data.</li>
        <li>Withdraw your consent for data processing at any time.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-medium text-text-primary mt-10 mb-4">Data Security and Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">We implement security measures to protect your information and retain your data only for as long as necessary to achieve the purposes outlined above.</p>

      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-medium text-text-primary mt-10 mb-4">Policy Updates</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We encourage you to review this page regularly.</p>

      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8]">For any questions or concerns about your data, please contact us at <a href="mailto:dpo@five-whys.com" class="text-accent underline">dpo@five-whys.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
